    <item>
      <title>美国服务业扩张速度创 2023 年 2 月以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-03/us-services-expand-at-fastest-pace-since-february-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国供应管理协会称，该协会的服务业指数上个月上涨了 3.4 点，至 54.9。最新数据超出了彭博社对经济学家的调查中的所有预测。Mike McKee 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-03/us-services-expand-at-fastest-pace-since-february-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 14:31:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着经济担忧加剧，土耳其股市进入熊市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/turkish-stocks-flirt-with-bear-market-as-economic-concerns-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势的最新升级，土耳其股市进入熊市，因股票对当地投资者的吸引力下降以及对经济前景的担忧，市场原本就低迷的情绪进一步加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/turkish-stocks-flirt-with-bear-market-as-economic-concerns-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 14:22:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
